What you need to know:  Kabeberi Sevens will pave way for the Christie 7s at the same venue on May 28 to 29 before the series heads to Mombasa for Driftwood Sevens on June 18 to 19.Dala Sevens will be held July 2 to 3 in Kisumu with the Prinsloo Sevens taking place on July 9 to 10 in Nakuru.The Kakamega Sevens, originally slated as the third leg of the series, will serve as the last leg on July 16 to 17 in Kakamega.